Havotron looked to his crew wondering why they weren't snapping to.
"WAKE UP!" He screamed. All of a sudden the window that had been
supporting Needlenose shattered in sending him flailing into the ship
straight for Spinister.  Quake stood and locked his knees in the
flight so as not to fall over.  Scrapper got to the controls and
pondered how to land.  "Havotron, my lord, I have found a large
geographical hieght sticking out of the ground on the island we are
heading at.  There is a solid H20 format on the top that proves to be
soft.  If we hit it we shall survive." Scrapper said.

"Very well, get to it everyone."
